    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:18.617" end="00:00:22.200">Uno, due. Uno, due, tre, quattro.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:22.278" end="00:00:23.520"/>
      <p begin="00:00:23.582" end="00:00:25.691">Se vi piace la musica di James Brown,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:25.691" end="00:00:27.585">questa serata vi piacer&#224;.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:27.585" end="00:00:29.761">Stasera si festeggiano i 62 anni di Black Velvet</p>
      <p begin="00:00:29.761" end="00:00:33.850">James Brown Junior!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:33.850" end="00:00:35.906" region="top">Whoo! 62! </p>
      <p begin="00:00:36.476" end="00:00:38.526" region="top">E allora adesso, battete le mani, </p>
      <p begin="00:00:38.526" end="00:00:39.758" region="top">perch&#232; abbiamo un giovane uomo </p>
      <p begin="00:00:39.758" end="00:00:41.545" region="top">che sta salendo sul palco. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:41.545" end="00:00:43.690">&#200; stato al David Letterman Show</p>
      <p begin="00:00:43.690" end="00:00:45.777">Applaudite, ecco a voi</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.777" end="00:00:49.963">Black Velvet James Brown Junior!</p>
      <p begin="00:00:49.963" end="00:00:52.279"/>
      <p begin="00:00:52.279" end="00:00:53.952"/>
      <p begin="00:00:53.952" end="00:00:59.249">&#9834; &#200; un mondo di uomini &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.249" end="00:01:05.556">&#9834; Ma io non sarei niente, niente... &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:01:05.556" end="00:01:06.715">Suono le canzoni di James Brown</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.715" end="00:01:13.956">da quando avevo 14 anni.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:13.956" end="00:01:16.475"/>
      <p begin="00:01:16.475" end="00:01:17.935"/>
      <p begin="00:01:17.935" end="00:01:21.271"/>
      <p begin="00:01:21.271" end="00:01:25.860"/>
      <p begin="00:01:25.860" end="00:01:29.767">Ma ora suoner&#242; Charles Bradley.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:29.767" end="00:01:52.445"/>
      <p begin="00:01:52.599" end="00:01:54.471" region="top">Il mio primo album di canzoni originali </p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.471" end="00:01:58.132" region="top">uscir&#224; il 25 di gennaio. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.132" end="00:02:01.271">Ho lottato per 42 anni</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.271" end="00:02:03.014">per cercare di farcela nell'industria musicale,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:03.014" end="00:02:04.731">e a 62 anni</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.731" end="00:02:06.775">sto iniziando a trovare la mia strada.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09.086" end="00:02:11.071">Non ho mai fatto abbastanza soldi</p>
      <p begin="00:02:11.071" end="00:02:13.928">per mantenermi nella musica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.928" end="00:02:15.993">Ma spero che questo album</p>
      <p begin="00:02:15.993" end="00:02:17.442">sia il mio punto di svolta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.442" end="00:02:20.252">che io possa mantenermi con la musica.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.314" end="00:02:26.837">Ehi, amico,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:26.837" end="00:02:28.808">ti porto dell'acqua, ok?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.808" end="00:02:30.155">Ehi, amico,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.155" end="00:02:30.834">questo &#232; il mio pappagallo.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:30.834" end="00:02:32.647">Mi fa arrabbiare.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:32.647" end="00:02:33.782">Mi arrabbio, me ne vado,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.782" end="00:02:35.520">vado nell'altra stanza, chiudo la porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.520" end="00:02:37.328">e lo lascio strillare quanto vuole.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.020" end="00:02:39.057">E ho un mio piccolo posto stabile,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:39.057" end="00:02:40.590">non &#232; quello che voglio,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.590" end="00:02:43.199">ma grazie a Dio ho un tetto sopra la testa.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:44.221" end="00:02:45.529">Quando entro nel mio piccolo appartamento</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.529" end="00:02:47.113">e chiudo la porta,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:47.113" end="00:02:48.734">sono in pace.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:48.734" end="00:02:50.496">Ma attraversare le case popolari,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:50.496" end="00:02:53.225">entrare nell'ascensore,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:53.225" end="00:02:54.307">arrivare l&#224;..</p>
      <p begin="00:02:54.307" end="00:02:55.545">&#232; l&#236; che iniziano i problemi.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.545" end="00:02:57.076">Non sai mai</p>
      <p begin="00:02:57.076" end="00:02:59.174">cosa pu&#242; succedere in quelle serate.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:59.174" end="00:03:00.663">Il ragazzo di sotto,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.663" end="00:03:01.666">si chiama Alfred.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:01.666" end="00:03:03.206">Un bravo ragazzo, non d&#224; fastidio a nessuno.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:03.206" end="00:03:04.783">Un ragazzo di chiesa.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:04.783" end="00:03:06.731">Hanno sparato al suo appartamento.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.731" end="00:03:07.753">Mi ha mostrato tutti i buchi</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.753" end="00:03:08.478">dove hanno sparato.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:08.478" end="00:03:09.261">Gli ho detto "wow, amico"</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.261" end="00:03:10.741">Gli ho detto</p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.741" end="00:03:13.017">"Uh, non potrei vivere al primo piano"</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13.017" end="00:03:14.586">Quando la situazione</p>
      <p begin="00:03:14.586" end="00:03:16.289">degenera nelle case popolari,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.289" end="00:03:18.007">vado a casa di mia madre</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.007" end="00:03:19.737">e dormo nel suo seminterrato.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:32.075" end="00:03:33.691">Dunque vengo qui</p>
      <p begin="00:03:33.691" end="00:03:36.011">e mi fermo la notte,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:36.011" end="00:03:37.269">fino al giorno dopo,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:37.269" end="00:03:39.058">quando vengo ad occuparmi dell'area,</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.058" end="00:03:40.105">a sistemare tutto</p>
      <p begin="00:03:40.105" end="00:03:43.638">per mantenere un tetto sopra le nostre teste.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:43.931" end="00:03:47.370">Mi piace fare delle palline</p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.370" end="00:03:48.964">di questo..</p>
      <p begin="00:03:50.953" end="00:03:53.302">Versarle qui.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:55.722" end="00:03:56.898">Ehi va bene cos&#236; il riso?</p>
      <p begin="00:03:57.067" end="00:03:58.366">Fammi vedere</p>
      <p begin="00:04:00.135" end="00:04:02.056">Ancora un po'.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:02.194" end="00:04:05.126">Vengo da una famiglia di 8 persone.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:05.188" end="00:04:08.021">Lo scopo principale &#232; tenere d'occhio tutto,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.021" end="00:04:11.799">&#232; mia madre e faccio del mio meglio.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.707" end="00:04:14.664" region="top">&#200; il mio bambino, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:14.664" end="00:04:16.777" region="top">e gli voglio bene. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.883" end="00:04:18.556" region="top">Mi lava i vestiti, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:18.726" end="00:04:19.466" region="top">pulisce questa casa. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.466" end="00:04:20.945" region="top">A San Valentino </p>
      <p begin="00:04:20.945" end="00:04:23.555" region="top">mi ha portato una scatola di caramelle. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:23.555" end="00:04:24.911" region="top">Dolce come quelle caramelle, </p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.911" end="00:04:26.138" region="top">ecco quant'&#232; dolce il mio bambino. </p>
      <p begin="00:04:26.138" end="00:04:27.835">Cerco solo</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.835" end="00:04:28.542">di rendere la sua vita tranquilla,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:28.542" end="00:04:29.668">e</p>
      <p begin="00:04:29.668" end="00:04:31.712">cos&#236; non si deve preoccupare</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.712" end="00:04:33.312">delle bollette e tutto il resto.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.312" end="00:04:34.478">Mi sono fatto carico di tutto,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.478" end="00:04:36.190">e davvero</p>
      <p begin="00:04:36.190" end="00:04:37.831">non sapevo a cosa andassi incontro.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.831" end="00:04:38.493">Ma ora ci sono dentro.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:38.493" end="00:04:40.083">Non cambier&#242;.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.083" end="00:04:41.252">Dunque l'unica cosa che posso fare</p>
      <p begin="00:04:41.252" end="00:04:42.968">&#232; cercar di far funzionare qualcosa,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.968" end="00:04:44.297">dove posso avere un'entrata decente</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.297" end="00:04:47.211">e posso vivere e lasciar vivere.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:47.211" end="00:04:50.030">Ed &#232; tutto, posso chiedere una vita adesso.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:50.138" end="00:04:56.875"/>
      <p begin="00:04:56.875" end="00:05:00.615">&#9834; Andiamo sempre in giro. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.615" end="00:05:05.222">&#9834; Dove fermarsi, nessuno lo sa &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:05.222" end="00:05:08.565">&#9834; &#200; un mondo freddo &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.965" end="00:05:12.469">&#9834; &#200; un mondo freddo &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:14.254" end="00:05:16.173">&#9834; Come possiamo fermare i cambiamenti &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:16.173" end="00:05:21.219">&#9834; che accadono oggigiorno in America? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:31.033" end="00:05:35.022">&#9834; Ohhh, ohhh, ohhhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.466" end="00:05:43.575">&#9834; Torna indietro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.575" end="00:05:47.287">&#9834; Torna indietro alla regola d'oro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:47.287" end="00:05:48.994">&#9834; Oh, ah, uh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.455" end="00:05:50.963">&#9834; torna indietro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:50.963" end="00:05:55.504">&#9834; Torna indietro alla regola d'oro &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:55.504" end="00:05:58.215">&#9834; Butta gi&#249; tutto &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.215" end="00:06:11.844"/>
      <p begin="00:06:11.844" end="00:06:13.438">Questa &#232; una canzone</p>
      <p begin="00:06:13.438" end="00:06:15.399">dal nuovo album, No time for dreaming.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:15.399" end="00:06:16.525">Charles Bradley</p>
      <p begin="00:06:16.525" end="00:06:17.652">e la Menahan Street Band.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:17.652" end="00:06:19.111">Non posso credere</p>
      <p begin="00:06:19.111" end="00:06:20.445">che tu sia spuntato dal nulla</p>
      <p begin="00:06:20.445" end="00:06:22.656">come uno sconosciuto virtuale per noi.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.656" end="00:06:24.858">Hai gi&#224; registrato in passato?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:24.981" end="00:06:26.277">No.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:26.277" end="00:06:28.820">&#200; la prima volta, veramente, che esco allo scoperto.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:28.820" end="00:06:30.349">So che ti sei esibito.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:30.349" end="00:06:31.431">S&#236;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:31.431" end="00:06:32.420">Come Black Velvet.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:32.420" end="00:06:34.044">S&#236;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:34.044" end="00:06:35.335">Ed ora ti esibisci</p>
      <p begin="00:06:35.335" end="00:06:37.064">come Charles Bradley?</p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.064" end="00:06:38.076">S&#236;, s&#236;.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:38.076" end="00:06:39.298">Beh, di certo hai una band eccezionale</p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.298" end="00:06:40.129">che ti supporta.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:40.129" end="00:06:41.667">E, ovviamente,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.667" end="00:06:43.302">la gente al Daptone,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:43.302" end="00:06:44.463">sai,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:44.463" end="00:06:45.287">che gran gruppo!</p>
      <p begin="00:06:45.287" end="00:06:46.597">E hai visto</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.597" end="00:06:49.276">cos'&#232; successo a Sharon Jones, S&#236;, s&#236;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49.276" end="00:06:51.340">Chi, sai, come te</p>
      <p begin="00:06:51.340" end="00:06:52.882">&#232; passato dall'oscurit&#224; totale,</p>
      <p begin="00:06:52.897" end="00:06:55.464">chiss&#224; quali vette potrai scalare.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.464" end="00:06:56.872">Quindi</p>
      <p begin="00:06:56.872" end="00:06:59.067">questo dev'essere un momento emozionante per te..</p>
      <p begin="00:06:59.067" end="00:07:01.820">Credo che Dio abbia ascoltato le mie preghiere,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.820" end="00:07:03.864">davvero, del tipo</p>
      <p begin="00:07:03.864" end="00:07:06.033">mi sono chiesto perch&#232; ci sia voluto cos&#236; tanto,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:06.033" end="00:07:07.451">ma non puoi mettere in discussione Dio,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:07.451" end="00:07:09.411">quando Lui voglia fare qualcosa.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:09.411" end="00:07:12.348">Dunque alla mia veneranda et&#224; ha iniziato a girare.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:12.348" end="00:07:13.916">Cosa succeder&#224;?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.916" end="00:07:15.375">Nel senso, pensi in grande?</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15.375" end="00:07:17.144">Credo che il cielo sia il limite.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:17.144" end="00:07:19.421">Congratulazioni per questo magnifico album.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:19.421" end="00:07:20.737">Non importa cosa succeder&#224;,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:20.737" end="00:07:22.632">&#232; davvero un lavoro sopraffino.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:22.632" end="00:07:24.943">Charles Bradley per WFUV.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:25.113" end="00:07:28.346"/>
      <p begin="00:07:28.346" end="00:07:33.685">&#9834; Questo mondo che ormai sta bruciando &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.685" end="00:07:39.107">&#9834; E nessuno che vuole prendersi la colpa &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:39.107" end="00:07:44.286">&#9834; Non dirmi come devo vivere la mia vita &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:44.286" end="00:07:49.746">&#9834; Quando non hai mai provato quel dolore &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:49.746" end="00:07:55.790">&#9834; Ohhhhh Ahhhh Ohhhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:55.790" end="00:07:58.335">&#9834; Ohhhhh &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:58.335" end="00:08:01.051">&#9834; Non mi vedono che piango? &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:01.051" end="00:08:02.883" region="top">&#9834; Ohhhhh &#9834; </p>
      <p begin="00:08:02.883" end="00:08:04.800"/>
      <p begin="00:08:04.800" end="00:08:06.051" region="top">Non so quanti artisti </p>
      <p begin="00:08:06.051" end="00:08:07.718" region="top">abbiano compiuto 62 anni </p>
      <p begin="00:08:07.718" end="00:08:09.445" region="top">e lanciato il loro primo album. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.213" end="00:08:11.950" region="top">Potrebbe essere il primo. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.777" end="00:08:14.936" region="top">Il ragazzo sta mettendo tutto in moto, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.936" end="00:08:16.937" region="top">per quanto mi riguarda. </p>
      <p begin="00:08:16.937" end="00:08:19.215" region="top">Ha lavorato sodo per tanto tempo, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:19.338" end="00:08:20.358" region="top">e spero </p>
      <p begin="00:08:20.358" end="00:08:21.734" region="top">che abbastanza persone riescano a sentirlo cantare, </p>
      <p begin="00:08:21.734" end="00:08:23.151">affinch&#232; possa avere</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.151" end="00:08:24.361">la vita che ha sempre desiderato</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24.361" end="00:08:26.139">e prendersi cura della sua famiglia.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:26.139" end="00:08:27.626"/>
      <p begin="00:08:27.626" end="00:08:30.701">&#9834; Uh, S&#236; &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.701" end="00:08:33.120">&#9834; Ti prendo, ragazza &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:33.120" end="00:08:34.538">&#9834; S&#236; &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:34.538" end="00:08:36.642">&#9834; Solo te &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:08:36.642" end="00:08:38.333">Sono andato da Gabe</p>
      <p begin="00:08:38.333" end="00:08:40.502">perch&#232; pensavo che sapesse cosa stesse facendo.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:40.502" end="00:08:42.129">Credevo che potesse darmi una mano</p>
      <p begin="00:08:42.129" end="00:08:44.673">ad entrare nell'industria musicale.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:44.673" end="00:08:48.569">L'unica cosa che sapevo fare era salire sul palco e suonare.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48.692" end="00:08:52.118">Se ti piace il funk e il soul, o l'afrobeat, e vivi a New York,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:52.226" end="00:08:55.036">Gabe Roth &#232; il ragazzo che vuoi nel retroscena.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:55.174" end="00:08:57.708">Questo &#232; il ragazzo che vuoi che ti indichi la strada da prendere,</p>
      <p begin="00:08:57.708" end="00:08:59.778">perch&#233; i suoi album erano fenomenali.</p>
